$1 \cdot y \equiv 462 \pmod{47}$
Now compute $462 \bmod 47$:
$47 \cdot 9 = 423$
$462 - 423 = 39$
So $y \equiv 39 \pmod{47}$

The smallest non-negative solution is $y = 39$.

